# ==========================================
# üîê FOUNDRY KEYSTORE SETUP GUIDE
# ==========================================
#
# FIRST TIME SETUP:
#   1. Import your private key to Foundry keystore (one-time):
#      cast wallet import green-goods-deployer --interactive
#      # You'll be prompted for your private key and password
#
#   2. Verify keystore was created:
#      cast wallet list
#      cast wallet address green-goods-deployer
#
#   3. Fund your deployer address with native tokens:
#      - Base Sepolia: https://www.coinbase.com/faucets/base-ethereum-goerli-faucet
#      - Sepolia: https://sepoliafaucet.com/
#
# SECURITY BENEFITS:
#   ‚úÖ Private key encrypted with password
#   ‚úÖ No plaintext keys in environment variables
#   ‚úÖ Interactive password prompt prevents automated access
#   ‚úÖ No risk of committing private keys to Git
#   ‚úÖ Command history doesn't expose credentials

# ==========================================
# üìö DEPLOYMENT COMMANDS
# ==========================================
#
# DEPLOY TO BASE SEPOLIA (Testnet):
#   pnpm deploy:base-sepolia:optimized
#   # You'll be prompted for keystore password
#
# DEPLOY TO OTHER NETWORKS:
#   pnpm deploy:celo:optimized           # Celo mainnet
#   pnpm deploy:sepolia                  # Ethereum Sepolia
#   pnpm deploy:arbitrum                 # Arbitrum mainnet
#   pnpm deploy:base                     # Base mainnet
#
# SCHEMA ONLY DEPLOYMENT:
#   pnpm deploy:schemas -- --network baseSepolia --broadcast
#
# DRY RUN (No broadcast):
#   pnpm deploy:dryrun:optimized -- --network baseSepolia
#
# CHECK DEPLOYMENT STATUS:
#   pnpm deployment:status

